OL,3,CNewcastle University academics vote
OL,4,Cfor industrial action amid #30m cuts
OL,6,FAcademics at Newcastle University have
OL,7,Fvoted to take industrial action amid
OL,8,F#30m in cuts and the institution's
OL,9,Finability to rule out compulsory job
OL,10,Flosses.
OL,12,FThe University and College Union (UCU)
OL,13,Fhas announced a successful ballot for
OL,14,Findustrial action at its Newcastle
OL,15,Fchapter, the Local Democracy Reporting
OL,16,FService reports.
