OL,3,CNewcastle University academics vote
OL,4,Cfor industrial action amid #30m cuts
OL,6,FAccording to the union, 83% of
OL,7,Fballoted members voted in favour of a
OL,8,Fstrike, with 88% stating they would be
OL,9,Fwilling to take action short of a
OL,10,Fstrike.
OL,12,FTensions between the union and
OL,13,Fmanagement have been evident since
OL,14,FSeptember 2024, when a #35m blackhole
OL,15,Fwas reported in the university's
OL,16,Fcoffers.
