OL,3,CNewcastle University academics vote
OL,4,Cfor industrial action amid #30m cuts
OL,6,FThe tens-of-millions drop in income
OL,7,Fwas largely attributed to a decline in
OL,8,Fthe number of international students,
OL,9,Fa common feature of university
OL,10,Ffinances across the UK.
OL,12,FThe #35m shortfall was initially
OL,13,Fcombated by mitigations, #15m of which
OL,14,Fhad already been built into the
OL,15,Fbudget, including recruitment freezes,
OL,16,Fa review into building projects, and
OL,17,Fsqueezed travel budgets.
