OL,3,CNewcastle University academics vote
OL,4,Cfor industrial action amid #30m cuts
OL,6,FBy October 2024, Newcastle University
OL,7,Fhad also paused academic job
OL,8,Fpromotions, cancelled pay reviews, and
OL,9,Flaunched a voluntary severance scheme.
OL,11,FAs the threat of strike action loomed
OL,12,Fover the university, bosses went on to
OL,13,Fsign off #30m in savings, including
OL,14,F#20m from the salary budget
OL,15,F(equivalent to 300 full time jobs),
OL,16,Fand stated that despite the expanded
OL,17,Fvoluntary severance scheme, could not
OL,18,Frule out mandatory job losses.
