OL,3,CNewcastle University academics vote
OL,4,Cfor industrial action amid #30m cuts
OL,6,FThe UCU has been balloting members
OL,7,Fsince 20 January 2025, calling for
OL,8,Faction.
OL,10,FMatt Perry, chair of Newcastle
OL,11,FUniversity UCU, said: "Higher
OL,12,FEducation is facing an unprecedented
OL,13,Fcrisis and it is clear that the high-
OL,14,Ftuition-fee funding model for UK
OL,15,FHigher Education is fundamentally
OL,16,Fbroken ` a model which has been
OL,17,Fchampioned by our own university's
OL,18,Fleaders.
