OL,3,CNewcastle University academics vote
OL,4,Cfor industrial action amid #30m cuts
OL,6,F"It has never been more important that
OL,7,Fwe campaign together for a new funding
OL,8,Fmodel which sees HE as an
OL,9,Findispensable public good, not a free
OL,10,Fmarket.
OL,12,F"There are huge amounts of anger
OL,13,Famongst staff and students about job
OL,14,Flosses and course closures. Ballots
OL,15,Ffor action are occurring up and down
OL,16,Fthe country. Dundee, Brunel, Kent,
OL,17,FSheffield, Cardiff, Newcastle,
OL,18,FSheffield Hallam: the resistance is
OL,19,Fspreading. Job losses should be a red
OL,20,Fline for every branch."
