OL,6,FCardiff University announced plans to
OL,7,Fcut 400 full time jobs alongside the
OL,8,Fpotential closure or merging of modern
OL,9,Flanguages, nursing, and music courses.
OL,11,FUni chiefs have also come under fire
OL,12,Fafter vice-chancellor Prof Chris Day,
OL,13,Ftalking at a conference abroad,
OL,14,Fannounced the institution was
OL,15,Fexploring opening a campus in India.
