OL,3,CNewcastle University academics vote
OL,4,Cfor industrial action amid #30m cuts
OL,6,FA Newcastle University spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are not immune to the
OL,8,Fchallenges currently affecting the UK
OL,9,Fhigher education sector and like many
OL,10,Funiversities, we are implementing a
OL,11,Frange of cost-saving measures to
OL,12,Fensure we remain in a sound financial
OL,13,Fposition.
OL,15,F"We want to work constructively with
OL,16,Four unions to build a more sustainable
OL,17,Ffuture for universities while
OL,18,Fsupporting our colleagues throughout
OL,19,Fthis challenging time."
